CatDescriptText: Rev. Charles Foggie was pastor of Wesley Center AME Church from 1944 to 1968, after which he became Bishop. He also headed the Pittsburgh Branch of the NAACP.
TitMainTitle: Two boys reaching down storm sewer outside Wesley Center AME Zion Church, Centre Avenue, Hill District
